"px", "size": 0, "sizes": [], "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "flex_direction": "column"}, "elements": [{"id": "12b096d", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "html", "settings": {"html": "<section class=\"hero\">\n<div class=\"hero-bg\"><img alt=\"Bride in a flowing designer wedding gown at Wife To Be, serving Chester and Cheshire\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"100vw\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1492175742197-ed20dc5a6bed?q=70&amp;w=1280&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop\" srcset=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1492175742197-ed20dc5a6bed?q=70&amp;w=640&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop 640w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1492175742197-ed20dc5a6bed?q=70&amp;w=960&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop 960w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1492175742197-ed20dc5a6bed?q=70&amp;w=1280&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop 1280w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1492175742197-ed20dc5a6bed?q=70&amp;w=1920&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop 1920w\"/></div>\n<div class=\"container\">\n<span class=\"brand-script\">Wife To Be</span>\n<h1>Designer Wedding Dresses for Chester &amp; Cheshire Brides</h1>\n<p>A calm, private and utterly personal way to find your gown. Two friendly Cheshire boutiques, hundreds of designer dresses, and a team who has done this beautifully for two decades.</p>\n<div class=\"hero-actions\">\n<a class=\"btn btn-gold\" data-testid=\"hero-book\" href=\"mailto:thegroupuk@yahoo.com?subject=Appointment%20Request\">Book Your Appointment</a>\n<a class=\"btn btn-light\" data-testid=\"hero-collections\" href=\"/bridal-collections/\">Browse The Gowns</a>\n</div>\n<p class=\"hero-meta\">Loved by brides in <span>Chester</span> \u00b7 Cheshire \u00b7 Wigan \u00b7 Frodsham \u00b7 Newton-le-Willows \u00b7 Bolton</p>\n</div>\n</section>"}, "elements": []}], "isInner": false}, {"id": "851052d", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "full", "width": {"unit": "%", "size": 100, "sizes": []}, "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 0, "sizes": [], "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "flex_direction": "column"}, "elements": [{"id": "ea5be35", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "html", "settings": {"html": "<section class=\"section\">\n<div class=\"container section-head reveal\">\n<span class=\"eyebrow\">More Than Just A Bridal Shop</span>\n<h2>Elegant \u00b7 Sophisticated \u00b7 Class</h2>\n<span class=\"divider\"></span>\n<p class=\"lead\">For more than twenty years we have welcomed brides from right across Cheshire \u2014 from the cobbled streets of Chester to the villages of the Cheshire plain \u2014 and helped each one uncover the gown that feels unmistakably hers.</p>\n<p class=\"muted\">There is no crush, no queue and no clock ticking. During your appointment the boutique belongs to you alone, so you can relax, take your time, and enjoy every moment of choosing the dress you will remember for the rest of your life.</p>\n</div>\n</section>"}, "elements": []}], "isInner": false}, {"id": "e971483", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "full", "width": {"unit": "%", "size": 100, "sizes": []}, "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 0, "sizes": [], "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "flex_direction": "column"}, "elements": [{"id": "71fa27a", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "html", "settings": {"html": "<section class=\"section band-ivory2\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"section-head reveal\">\n<span class=\"eyebrow\">Our Designers</span>\n<h2>Four Celebrated Bridal Houses</h2>\n<span class=\"divider\"></span>\n<p class=\"muted\">As an official stockist for some of the most respected names in bridal, our hand-picked collection brings together four distinctive designers \u2014 so every bride finds a style that speaks to her.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cards\">\n<article class=\"card reveal\">\n<div class=\"card-img\"><img alt=\"Sophia Tolli bohemian lace wedding dress with fitted bodice - designer bridal gowns at Wife To Be, Chester &amp; Cheshire\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"__WTB_BASE__/assets/sophia-tolli-1.webp\"/></div>\n<div class=\"card-body\"><span class=\"eyebrow\">Sophia Tolli</span><h3>Softly Romantic</h3><p class=\"muted\">Flattering silhouettes, delicate lacework and beautifully engineered bodices that move with you.</p></div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"card reveal\">\n<div class=\"card-img\"><img alt=\"Veni Infantino statement designer wedding dress with luxurious fabric - available at Wife To Be bridal boutique, Cheshire\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"__WTB_BASE__/assets/veni-infantino.jpeg\"/></div>\n<div class=\"card-body\"><span class=\"eyebrow\">Veni Infantino</span><h3>Quietly Bold</h3><p class=\"muted\">Contemporary statement gowns with luxurious fabrics for the bride who wants a considered, confident entrance.</p></div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"card reveal\">\n<div class=\"card-img\"><img alt=\"Phoenix Gowns beaded V-neck A-line wedding dress with flowing chiffon skirt - designer bridal gowns at Wife To Be, Chester &amp; Cheshire\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"__WTB_BASE__/assets/phoenix-gowns-1.webp\"/></div>\n<div class=\"card-body\"><span class=\"eyebrow\">Phoenix Gowns</span><h3>Made Around You</h3><p class=\"muted\">Classic, expertly cut dresses with adaptable details, so your gown ends up feeling entirely one-of-a-kind.</p></div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"card reveal\">\n<div class=\"card-img\"><img alt=\"White Rose designer wedding gown - White Rose &amp; White Rose Plus bridal collection at Wife To Be, Cheshire\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"__WTB_BASE__/assets/white-rose-1.jpg\"/></div>\n<div class=\"card-body\"><span class=\"eyebrow\">White Rose &amp; Plus</span><h3>For Every Figure</h3><p class=\"muted\">Beautifully made gowns, including a dedicated plus-size range crafted to flatter and celebrate every shape.</p></div>\n</article>\n</div>\n<div class=\"center\" style=\"margin-top:46px\"><a class=\"btn\" data-testid=\"home-view-designers\" href=\"/bridal-collections/\">See The Full Collection</a></div>\n</div>\n</section>"}, "elements": []}], "isInner": false}, {"id": "067cee8", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "full", "width": {"unit": "%", "size": 100, "sizes": []}, "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 0, "sizes": [], "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "flex_direction": "column"}, "elements": [{"id": "664b6c1", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "html", "settings": {"html": "<section class=\"section\">\n<div class=\"container split\">\n<div class=\"framed reveal\"><img alt=\"Inside the Wife To Be bridal boutique with rails of designer gowns\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1621369663005-68a558655fad?q=80&amp;w=900&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop\"/></div>\n<div class=\"reveal\">\n<span class=\"eyebrow\">The Experience</span>\n<h2>Where Your Wedding Story Begins</h2>\n<span class=\"divider left\"></span>\n<p>With more than 200 gowns on the rails, ours is one of the widest choices you will find in the region. Whether you arrive with a folder of ideas or a completely open mind, there is every chance the dress is already here waiting for you.</p>\n<p class=\"muted\">Our stylists know their gowns inside out and will happily talk you through fabrics, shapes and finishing touches \u2014 guiding, never pushing, until you find the one that makes you catch your breath.</p>\n<a class=\"btn btn-gold\" data-testid=\"split-book\" href=\"/contact/\">Reserve A Private Appointment</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>"}, "elements": []}], "isInner": false}, {"id": "6c31f43", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "full", "width": {"unit": "%", "size": 100, "sizes": []}, "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 0, "sizes": [], "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "flex_direction": "column"}, "elements": [{"id": "67ea6c5", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "html", "settings": {"html": "<section class=\"section band-blush\">\n<div class=\"container stats\">\n<div class=\"stat reveal\"><div class=\"num\">20+</div><div class=\"lbl\">Years Dressing Brides</div></div>\n<div class=\"stat reveal\"><div class=\"num\">200+</div><div class=\"lbl\">Gowns On The Rails</div></div>\n<div class=\"stat reveal\"><div class=\"num\">4</div><div class=\"lbl\">Designer Houses</div></div>\n<div class=\"stat reveal\"><div class=\"num\">2</div><div class=\"lbl\">Cheshire Boutiques</div></div>\n</div>\n</section>"}, "elements": []}], "isInner": false}, {"id": "4233f06", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "full", "width": {"unit": "%", "size": 100, "sizes": []}, "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 0, "sizes": [], "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "flex_direction": "column"}, "elements": [{"id": "9bbf1ab", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "html", "settings": {"html": "<section class=\"section\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"section-head reveal\"><span class=\"eyebrow\">What Our Brides Say</span><h2>Trusted By Cheshire Brides</h2><span class=\"divider\"></span></div>\n<div class=\"grid\" style=\"grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(280px,1fr))\">\n<div class=\"quote reveal\"><div class=\"stars\">\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605</div><p>I genuinely dreaded dress shopping and left grinning from ear to ear. Calm, kind and not a hint of pressure \u2014 I found mine in Chester's favourite little boutique.</p><div class=\"who\">Lauren \u00b7 Chester</div></div>\n<div class=\"quote reveal\"><div class=\"stars\">\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605</div><p>Worth the trip from Wigan and then some. The choice was huge and the styling advice was honest \u2014 exactly what I needed.</p><div class=\"who\">Katie \u00b7 Wigan</div></div>\n<div class=\"quote reveal\"><div class=\"stars\">\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605</div><p>They listened, they remembered the little details, and they never once rushed me. I felt completely looked after from start to finish.</p><div class=\"who\">Rachel \u00b7 Frodsham</div></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"center\" style=\"margin-top:46px\"><a class=\"btn\" data-testid=\"home-view-brides\" href=\"/brides/\">Read More Reviews</a></div>\n</div>\n</section>"}, "elements": []}], "isInner": false}, {"id": "8afe86b", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "full", "width": {"unit": "%", "size": 100, "sizes": []}, "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 0, "sizes": [], "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "flex_direction": "column"}, "elements": [{"id": "90d2037", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "html", "settings": {"html": "<section class=\"cta\">\n<div class=\"cta-bg\"><img alt=\"Elegant bride on her wedding day\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"100vw\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1722805740302-7bf173339b80?q=70&amp;w=1280&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop\" srcset=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1722805740302-7bf173339b80?q=70&amp;w=640&amp;aut